<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.5">
<l>tammāmaṉ nantakō pālaṉ taḻīik koṇ ṭeṉmakaḷ taṉṉai</l>
<l>cemmānti rēyeṉṟu collic ceḻuṅkayaṟ kaṇṇuñcev vāyum</l>
<l>kommai mulaiyu miṭaiyum koḻumpaṇait tōḷkaḷuṅ kaṇṭiṭṭu</l>
<l>immaka ḷaippeṟṟa tāya riṉittari yāreṉṉuṅ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Nanda Gopāla, her uncle, embracing [her],</l>
<l rend="indent">saying “You are appropriate”,</l>
<l>seeing [her] beautiful kayal eyes, red lips,</l>
<l rend="indent">round breasts, waist, and plump bamboo arms,</l>
<l>will think,</l>
<l rend="indent">“how can the mother who begot this girl carry on now?”,</l>
<l>won’t he?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
